    "html": "<DOCUMENT>\n<TYPE>EX-99.1\n<SEQUENCE>2\n<FILENAME>exhibit991.htm\n<DESCRIPTION>EXHIBIT 99.1\n<TEXT>\n\n\n\n<HTML>\n<HEAD>\n   <TITLE>Silver Wheaton Corp.: Exhibit 99.1 - Filed by newsfilecorp.com</TITLE>\n\n</HEAD>\n\n<BODY style=\"font-size:10pt;\">\n\n<HR noshade align=\"center\" width=100% size=3 color=\"black\">\n\n\n<!--$$/page=-->\n<p align=\"right\"><b>Exhibit 99.1</b><A name=\"page_1\"></A></p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n\n<IMG src=\"exhibit991x1x1.jpg\" border=0 width=\"526\" height=\"91\">\n<BR>\n</p>\n<TABLE style=\"font-size:10pt;border-color:black;border-collapse:collapse;\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" border=\"0\"><TR valign=\"top\">\n\t<TD align=left width=\"50%\">\nFOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE\n\t</TD>\n\t<TD width=\"50%\" align=right>\nTSX:SLW\n\t</TD>\n</TR>\n<TR valign=\"top\">\n\t<TD align=left width=\"50%\">\nMay 21, 2013\n\t</TD>\n\t<TD width=\"50%\" align=right>\nNYSE:SLW\n\t</TD>\n</TR>\n</TABLE>\n<P align=\"center\">\n<B>SILVER WHEATON ANNOUNCES ELECTION OF DIRECTORS </B></P>\n<P align=\"justify\">\nVancouver, British Columbia &ndash; Silver Wheaton Corp. (&ldquo;Silver Wheaton&rdquo; or the &ldquo;Company&rdquo;) (TSX:SLW) (NYSE:SLW) announces that the nominees listed in the management proxy circular for the 2013 Annual and Special Meeting of\nShareholders were elected as directors of Silver Wheaton. Detailed results of the vote for directors of the Company held at the Annual and Special Meeting of Shareholders earlier today, are shown below: </P>\n<TABLE style=\"font-size:10pt;border-collapse:collapse; font-family:Times New Roman\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" border=\"1\" bordercolor=\"#000000\"><TR valign=\"top\">\n\t<TD align=left style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #000000; border-left-color:#000000; border-right-color:#000000; border-top-color:#000000\">\n<p style=\"margin-left: 5pt\">\n<B><font size=\"2\">Nominee</font></B><font size=\"2\">\n\t</TD>\n\t<TD width=13% align=center style=\"bor