=center style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #000000; border-left-color:#000000; border-right-color:#000000; border-top-color:#000000\">\n164,520,490\n\t</TD>\n\t<TD width=13% align=center style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #000000; border-left-color:#000000; border-right-color:#000000; border-top-color:#000000\">\n98.67%\n\t</TD>\n\t<TD width=13% align=center style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #000000; border-left-color:#000000; border-right-color:#000000; border-top-color:#000000\">\n2,223,304\n\t</TD>\n\t<TD width=13% align=center style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #000000; border-left-color:#000000; border-right-color:#000000; border-top-color:#000000\">\n1.33% </font>\n\t</TD>\n</TR>\n</TABLE>\n<P align=\"justify\">\nIn addition, the non-binding advisory resolution accepting the Company&rsquo;s approach to executive compensation was carried with 93.87% of the votes cast in favour of such resolution. </P>\n<P align=\"justify\">\nFor further information, please contact: </P>\n<P align=\"justify\">\nPatrick Drouin <BR>\nVice President, Investor Relations<BR>\nSilver Wheaton Corp. <BR>\nTel: 1-800-380-8687 <BR>\nEmail: <U><FONT color=\"#0000ff\">info@silverwheaton.com</FONT></U> <BR>\nWebsite: <U><FONT color=\"#0000ff\">www.silverwheaton.com</FONT></U> <BR>\n</P>\n\n<HR noshade align=\"center\" width=\"100%\" size=5 color=\"black\">\n\n\n</BODY>\n\n</HTML>\n</TEXT>\n</DOCUMENT>\n"
